<h1 class="story_title">HTML5 Oblique Strategies</h1>
<div class="homepage_story">
	<p class="story"><a href="http://oblique.pointlineplane.co.uk">An online Oblique Strategies deck</a>. I’m sure there are other online Oblique Strategies decks but I expect very few of them will have been tested so scantly and on such a small range of browsers. This one takes advantage of HTML5 local storage so your browser should remember where in a shuffled deck you’ve got to (if you’re using Chrome, Safari or Firefox, recent versions).</a>
